Feline::

She turned and glared at HotRod. "I'm not going to let you reprogram 
me into a maximal just so that you can have me! You left me. And when 
you did that, you tore my world apart. I won't let you live with the 
satisfaction of gloating to your scum sucking maximal friends that 
you hurt a predacon like me."  SHe pulled out a quazar pistol and pt 
it to her head. Tears ran down her cheek. "You think it hurt! It hurt 
like the pit. Now go there yourself."  She fired 5 blasts at HotRod, 
aiming at his chest. Then, she turned the pistol on herself. BANG!!

Her lifeless body fell to the ground. Her optics still open, but 
dark.  She had a large hole in the side of her cranium and leaking 
mech fluid heavily. 

OOC: Put Feline on the deceased list.
